<help battle consider>

This command allows you to get some idea of what an opponent
might be able to do to you.  This is somewhat obvious to
many players, and they may not take your probing lightly!  It
is known to be unreliable, but it may offer you good information
at times!!

Syntax:  consider <<i_th> [critter]

Example:  consider priest

<color = blue>
See Also:  hit, flee, assist, abilities, assist
</color></help>
